item.content:encoded:
Remember that the CFP will end on Feb 29th, so hurry up and don’t miss the chance to be part of jsDay 2016! Please remember that the jsDay is an international conference, so session proposals must be in English.

Tickets are available, get one at the discounted early bird price until they last!

Do you want to be part of jsDay 2016 as a sponsor? Take a look to our sponsorship options!
